The poignant testimonies of Russian soldiers returning from Ukraine
subhed: 'My Undesirable Friends: Part I − Last Air in Moscow,' a film by two independent Russian journalists from Novaya Gazeta, gives voice to 18 soldiers returning from the front. Far from spouting Kremlin propaganda, they express their doubts. In just six months, the documentary has been viewed 1.5 million times in Russia.

title: The mysterious 'knocker' scaring elderly women in a Brittany town
subhed: For more than two years, a prowler has been knocking on doors and shutters during the night in a village in Brittany, France, creating a climate of fear among his preferred targets: elderly women. Authorities were slow to take the case seriously.
